name: Jau-Shin Lou, MD
description: Dr. Jau-Shin Lou practices neurology and treats conditions such as neuromuscular diseases, neuropathy, and myopathy. He is the Roger Gilbertson Endowed Chair in Neurology at UND School of Medicine and Health Sciences and Sanford Health. He speaks English and Chinese (Taiwanese)
